[04/02/2018 13:29:04] <font color="#00ff00">Muchísimos.</font>
[04/02/2018 13:29:07] <font color="#00ff00">Voy a conocer al cultivador</font>
[04/02/2018 13:29:07] <font color="#00ff00">de almendros, David Phippen.</font>
