[04/02/2018 13:29:13] <font color="#00ff00">Hola.</font>
[04/02/2018 13:29:14] <font color="#ffffff">-¿Cómo te va?</font>
[04/02/2018 13:29:15] <font color="#00ff00">¿Eres David?</font>
